thread.title: Police raid home of ousted Malaysian leader

title: Police raid home of ousted Malaysian leader
text:
Police raid home of ousted Malaysian leader 11:39am BST - 01:27
At least a dozen police officers enter the family home of ousted Malaysian Prime Minister Najib Razak, who has been dogged since 2015 by a multi-billion-dollar scandal. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
